Package: scen
Title: Client for the Taiwan Tourism Administration Statistics Database
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("scen", "contributors", email = "yuyou.liou@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A programmatic client for the Tourism Statistics Database of the
    Taiwan Tourism Administration (stat.taiwan.net.tw). Provides functions to
    download visitor counts for the major scenic / recreational spots
    (the main purpose of the package), as well as inbound visitor arrivals,
    outbound traveller departures and cruise visitor data, including the
    finest cross-tabulations exposed by the site (e.g. age x gender x purpose).
    The package reproduces the site's request-signing scheme, handles the
    server's rate limiting with throttling and exponential back-off, and caches
    successful responses on disk.
